{
  "comment": "Native-image metadata for Apache MINA sshd (AWS Transfer connector SFTP client, SftpConnectorClient). MINA: (a) builds JDK dynamic proxies for its event-listener interfaces; (b) loads its security-provider registrar + NIO IO factory reflectively by name; (c) builds JCA SecurityEntityFactory wrappers by reflectively locating getInstance(...) on the JCA entity classes. The runtime registrar list is pinned to BouncyCastle (see SftpConnectorClient) to avoid SunJCE / net.i2p-EdDSA probing.",
